name: Kirk Kaleidoscopic
description:
Edition 1 of 1

Kirk Kaleidoscope is a changing symmetrical pattern from small pieces of colored candles, temples, bubbles and more. A kaleidoscope symbolizes energy from creativity and allows you to see life in a bigger or smaller form. The colors and forms in the Kirk Kaleidoscope symbolize you escaping or trying to regain time. Audio by Dieter Hofmann. Portion of proceeds will be donated to the Beckley Foundation who are leaders in scientific research into psychoactive substances.
